{"pageProps":{"page":{"slug":"discography","title":"Discography | Agust Islandia · Agust Smari Bjarkarson","description":"Full discography for Agust Islandia (Agust Smari Bjarkarson): every album, EP, single, and special release, with links to lyrics and streaming.","canonical":"/discography.html","routePath":"/discography.html","language":"en-US","og":{"title":"Discography | Agust Islandia · Agust Smari Bjarkarson","description":"Complete catalog of albums, EPs, singles, and special releases by Agust Islandia (Agust Smari Bjarkarson), Icelandic queer pop artist.","image":"/the-unseen-chorus-cover.webp","type":"website","url":"/discography.html"},"twitter":{"card":"summary_large_image","title":"Discography | Agust Islandia · Agust Smari Bjarkarson","description":"Complete catalog of albums, EPs, singles, and special releases by Agust Islandia.","image":"/the-unseen-chorus-cover.webp"},"mainEntity":{"id":"/discography.html#release-list","type":"ItemList"},"bodyHtml":"<header class=\"hub-hero\">\n      <section class=\"hub-hero-copy\">\n        <span class=\"hub-kicker\">Full Catalogue</span>\n        <h1>Discography</h1>\n        <p class=\"hub-subtitle\">\n          Every album, EP, single, and special release by <strong>Agust Smari Bjarkarson</strong>,\n          performing as <strong>Agust Islandia</strong>. Newest first. Each title opens its own\n          page with cover art, tracklist, lyrics, and streaming links.\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"hub-actions\">\n          <a class=\"hub-btn hub-btn-primary\" href=\"/lyrics.html\">All lyrics</a>\n          <a class=\"hub-btn hub-btn-secondary\" href=\"https://music.apple.com/us/artist/agust-smari-bjarkarson/1827272561\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Apple Music</a>\n          <a class=\"hub-btn hub-btn-secondary\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/artist/3vCWdArvNjajk3eCmfExNG\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Spotify</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hub-highlights\">\n          <div class=\"hub-highlight\">\n            <strong>14 releases</strong>\n            <span>5 albums &amp; EPs, 5 singles, 4 special releases.</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"hub-highlight\">\n            <strong>Latest</strong>\n            <span>The Unseen Chorus, a 27-track gay musical (Oct 2025).</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"hub-highlight\">\n            <strong>Breakout</strong>\n            <span>Gay and Proud / Gay y Orgulloso — bilingual Pride anthem, 540K+ TikTok.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <aside class=\"hub-summary-card\" aria-labelledby=\"hub-summary-title\">\n        <div>\n          <h2 id=\"hub-summary-title\">At a glance</h2>\n          <p>Four years of queer pop and theatrical songwriting, from Pride anthems to full-length gay musicals.</p>\n        </div>\n        <ul>\n          <li>2 full gay musicals, 1 EP</li>\n          <li>5 singles, bilingual &amp; English</li>\n          <li>~59 lyric pages published</li>\n          <li>Streaming on every major platform</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"hub-link-row\">\n          <a class=\"hub-btn hub-btn-secondary\" href=\"/the-unseen-chorus.html\">The Unseen Chorus</a>\n          <a class=\"hub-btn hub-btn-secondary\" href=\"/gay-and-proud.html\">Gay and Proud</a>\n        </div>\n      </aside>\n    </header>\n\n    <main id=\"main-content\" class=\"hub-grid\">\n\n      <section class=\"hub-panel hub-panel-wide\" aria-labelledby=\"albums-heading\">\n        <div class=\"hub-panel-inner\">\n          <h2 id=\"albums-heading\">Albums &amp; EPs</h2>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Gay Musical · 27 tracks · 6 October 2025</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/the-unseen-chorus.html\">The Unseen Chorus</a></h3>\n            <p>Three-act narrative album moving from infidelity through sexual addiction into recovery and redemptive love. Full lyrics published for every track.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">EP · 5 tracks · 2 September 2025</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/cowboys.html\">Cowboys</a></h3>\n            <p>Queer country-pop with teeth. Subverts western tropes into something unapologetically gay, campy, and tender.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Gay Musical · 22 tracks · 18 July 2025</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/swipe-me-to-the-moon.html\">Swipe Me to the Moon</a></h3>\n            <p>Modern queer love story told through dating apps, first dates, the grind, the spiral, and the long negotiation of what real connection costs. 16 tracks have dedicated lyric pages.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">EP · 5 tracks · 16 July 2025</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/pride-month-2025.html\">Pride Month 2025</a></h3>\n            <p>Landing page collecting the Pride Month releases from 2025.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Musical · In development</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/the-gay-mormon-musical.html\">The Gay Mormon Musical</a></h3>\n            <p>Landing page for the upcoming musical project.</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"hub-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"singles-heading\">\n        <div class=\"hub-panel-inner\">\n          <h2 id=\"singles-heading\">Singles</h2>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Bilingual single · 11 September 2025</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/gay-and-proud.html\">Gay and Proud / Gay y Orgulloso</a></h3>\n            <p>The breakout Pride anthem. English and Spanish versions with full lyrics. 540,000+ TikTok views.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Single · 15 August 2025</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/bless-this-mess.html\">Bless This Mess</a></h3>\n            <p>A hymn to chaos, self-acceptance, and being kind to your own unfinished life.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Single</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/out-and-proud.html\">Out and Proud</a></h3>\n            <p>An uptempo statement of visibility.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Bilingual single</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/my-fire.html\">My Fire (Mi Fuego)</a></h3>\n            <p>English and Spanish versions of a dance-pop track about desire that refuses to dim.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Single · EDM dance</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/feel-alive.html\">Feel Alive</a></h3>\n            <p>Dance anthem built for the floor.</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"hub-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"specials-heading\">\n        <div class=\"hub-panel-inner\">\n          <h2 id=\"specials-heading\">Special releases</h2>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Thematic release</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/peach-and-purple.html\">Peach and Purple</a></h3>\n            <p>A one-off thematic release.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Pride release</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/pride-on-the-seas.html\">Pride on the Seas</a></h3>\n            <p>A Pride-themed release set on the water.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Global Pride</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/pride-around-the-world.html\">Pride Around the World</a></h3>\n            <p>A global Pride-facing release.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"hub-release-item\">\n            <span class=\"hub-release-meta\">Left-field</span>\n            <h3><a href=\"/yogurt.html\">Yogurt</a></h3>\n            <p>A standalone release off the beaten path.</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"hub-panel hub-panel-wide\" aria-labelledby=\"lyrics-heading\">\n        <div class=\"hub-panel-inner\">\n          <h2 id=\"lyrics-heading\">Looking for the lyrics?</h2>\n          <p>Every release above links through to its own page. For the full A-to-Z lyric archive, grouped by album, open the lyrics index.</p>\n          <div class=\"hub-link-row\">\n            <a class=\"hub-btn hub-btn-primary\" href=\"/lyrics.html\">Open the lyrics archive</a>\n            <a class=\"hub-btn hub-btn-secondary\" href=\"/about.html\">About the musician</a>\n            <a class=\"hub-btn hub-btn-secondary\" href=\"/contact.html\">Contact</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>","schemaGraph":{"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":"CollectionPage","@id":"https://www.gusti.com/discography.html#webpage","url":"https://www.gusti.com/discography.html","name":"Discography | Agust Islandia · Agust Smari Bjarkarson","description":"Full discography for Agust Islandia (Agust Smari Bjarkarson): every album, EP, single, and special release.","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#website"},"about":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#agust-person"},"mainEntity":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/discography.html#release-list"},"breadcrumb":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/discography.html#breadcrumb"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#organization"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https://www.gusti